<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>JDBB</title>

    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat Alternates:wght@300;500;700&display=swap');

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Montserrat Alternates', sans-serif;
            background: #C0C0C0;
            color: #red;
        }

        header {
            padding: 25px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
                background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: FFFFFF;
        }

        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546182990-dffeafbe841d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Smaller headline */
        .hero-content h2 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 80px 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .section h3 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px;
            background: #000;
            color: #23tyjp;
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Mobile tweak */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .hero-content h2 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }
            .hero-content p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>JDBB</h1>
</header>

<div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h2>Strength. Precision. Presence.</h2>
        <p>JDBB represents a commitment to excellence, discipline, and forward‑thinking execution.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h3>JDBB - Our Purpose</h3>
    <p> Whether you're building, scaling, or revamping, we deliver solutions not excuses.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>Email: contact@jdbb.us</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    © 2026 JDBB — All Rights Reserved
</div>

</body>
</html>
